## Decisions Made
- Port wi skill to a Python script that emits native_task_sync stdout hint instead of calling TaskCreate/TaskUpdate directly (per spec Native Task Sync 패턴).
- Keep status mapping table (WI_STATUS_TO_NATIVE) inside the script rather than importing from a shared module — the table is small and stable.
- The harness checks existence for ALL expected scripts up front; per-script blocks gate on `[ -x ]` so partial commits surface clear FAIL lines for missing scripts and PASS lines for completed ones.

