## Constraints Identified
- Scripts cannot call TaskCreate/TaskUpdate (LLM-only); they emit hints. The Orchestrator/State Manager executes them after parsing stdout.
- depends_on immutability must be enforced on upsert (rule 8 in wi-schema.md).

